Author: cipi#4502
Content:
`I feel BCH is going to outgrow BTC if they don't raise the blocklimit and stop focussing on LN`
BCH only works as long as there is a blockreward, because the txfees are like 0 and as such the miners only mine the chain because of the blockreward... when its gone, the miners will be gone
BTC thinks more longterm... after the blockreward will end, the idea is that the miners will continue to mine only with the txfees as reward
